window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>She is the perfect assassin.</p> <p>A Russian orphan, saved from the death penalty for the brutal revenge she took on her gangster father's killers.</p> <p>Ruthlessly trained. Given a new life. New names, new faces - whichever fits.</p> <p>Her paymasters call themselves The Twelve. But she knows nothing of them. Konstantin is the man who saved her and the one she answers to.</p> <p>She is Villanelle. Without conscience. Without guilt. Without weakness.</p> <p>Eve Polastri is the woman who hunts her. MI5, until one error of judgment costs her everything.</p> <p>Then stopping a ruthless assassin becomes more than her job. It becomes personal.</p>"; 
